data: {"p":"response/fragments/-1/results","v":[{"url":"https://www.leisu.com/news/view-578542","title":"国际友谊前瞻：安帅率巴西战死敌，法国队近7场保持不败","snippet":"在过去的2届世界杯上，法国队获得1次冠军和1次亚军。在美加墨世界杯上，兵强马壮的高卢雄鸡，无疑仍然将是夺冠热门，也将为获得队史第3座世界杯冠军的目标而战。","cite_index":1,"published_at":1774454400.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/leisu.com","site_name":"雷速体育","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/soccer/2026-FIFA-World-Cup-Spain-lead-ESPN-s-rankings-as-favorites-2027229","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup: Spain lead ESPN's rankings as favorites","snippet":"contenders. Topping the list is Spain, a nation that has won the World Cup once, in 2010. Spain’s recent resurgence, highlighted by strong performances in international competitions, signals a return to elite status. ... two-time world champions (1998, 2018)...","cite_index":2,"published_at":1774281600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/ghanaweb.com","site_name":"GhanaWeb","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://sn.ifeng.com/c/8rkgWf9MtaO","title":"2026世界杯前瞻：365体育分析三强鼎立，北美亚洲新篇章——当足球盛宴首次跨越三国，48支劲旅将如何重绘世界足坛版图？","snippet":"夺冠热门巡礼：新旧势力的巅峰对决 ... 三、 东道主表现：美加墨的足球野望 本届世界杯的三位东道主，不仅是赛事的组织者，更是积极的参与者。 美国队： 坐拥主场之利，美国队近年来进步神速。普利希奇...","cite_index":3,"published_at":1774281600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/ifeng.com","site_name":"凤凰网","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.si.com/soccer/world-cup-2026-power-rankings-spain-argentina-favorites-norway-dark-horses","title":"World Cup 2026 Power Rankings: Spain & Argentina Favorites, Norway the Dark Horses","snippet":"Here, Sports Illustrated unveils its 2026 World Cup Power Rankings, breaking down the 20 leading contenders based on qualifying form, momentum, squad strength and everything else in between. ## 20. Uruguay ... 18. Switzerland ... 16. Belgium","cite_index":4,"published_at":1773936000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/si.com","site_name":"Sports Illustrated","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://www.foxsports.com/stories/soccer/2026-world-cup-power-rankings-why-colombia-belongs-top-5","title":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: Why Colombia Belongs In the Top 5","snippet":"11: #10 United States previously unranked FIFA Rank: 15 ... It’s not crazy to put USA here in the top-10. In the FIFA Rankings, the U.S. is at 15th, but again, this isn’t just a World Cup...","cite_index":5,"published_at":1772640000.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/foxsports.com","site_name":"FOX Sports","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://m.qtx.com/worldcup/276955.html","title":"今年世界杯冠亚季军预测 西班牙成最大热门","snippet":"2026年美加墨世界杯的冠亚季军争夺，大概率仍将集中在欧洲传统豪强与少数南美劲旅之间，西班牙、法国、英格兰三支球队成为冠亚季军的热门人选，这一预测也贴合当前足坛的实力格局与主流夺冠赔率走向，各支球队的竞争优势与潜在短板，也决定了其在世界杯赛场的大概率走势。","cite_index":6,"published_at":1771430400.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/qtx.com","site_name":"球天下","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://www.thedailystar.net/sports/football/news/2026-fifa-world-cup-how-favourites-stack-4050361","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup: How the favourites stack up","snippet":"Ahead of Friday's 2026 World Cup draw, here we take a look at the leading contenders at the first-ever 48-team finals to take place across North America next June and July (current world ranking in brackets): ## Spain (1)","cite_index":7,"published_at":1764777600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/thedailystar.net","site_name":"The Daily Star","query_indexes":[2]},{"url":"https://m.qtx.com/others/275126.html","title":"2026年美加墨是世界杯四强预测 西班牙、阿根廷等队最被看好","snippet":"2026年美加墨世界杯四强预测中，西班牙、法国、英格兰和卫冕冠军阿根廷是最被看好的球队。首先是卫冕冠军阿根廷，此前的世界杯南美区预选赛，阿根廷以南美区第一的身份强势出线。梅西依然是目前这支阿根廷队的绝对核心...","cite_index":8,"published_at":1766851200.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/qtx.com","site_name":"球天下","query_indexes":[0]},{"url":"https://mauth.cbssports.com/soccer/news/2026-world-cup-power-rankings-usmnt-argentina-spain-brazil-mexico/","title":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: USMNT close to top 10; Lionel Messi's Argentina not No. 1","snippet":"2026 World Cup Power Rankings: USMNT close to top 10; Lionel Messi's Argentina not No. 1 ## The 2026 World Cup will take place next year in the United States, Mexico and Canada","cite_index":9,"published_at":1763481600.0,"site_icon":"https://cdn.deepseek.com/site-icons/cbssports.com","site_name":"CBS Sports","query_indexes":[2]}]}

